title: Koi ni Naranai Wake ga Nai
original_name: 恋にならないワケがない
sinopse:
Koizumi Nene is bored by the mundane quality of her life, every day being the same, until she has a chance encounter with college student Sakuraba Hajime. And now he's her neighbor too! Were they fated to meet one another?

(Source: Lemonade Scans)
